Ke3 - I thought I had escaped the discovered check but alas, left my f2 pawn en prise to the Wicked Witch of the West who waves her wand, turns it to dust and cackles check in the ear of King Henry.  I either have to walk Henry back into that discovery or Cop Old Matey by playing Henry to f4 and allowing e5#, or Option C, wave the white flag.  I chose Option C.  I must now start working on my tactics even though I have increased my games workload.  All I can say is, it has been, er erm, a voyage of discovery!
